"<guimenuitem>End of the document</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"អ្នក​អាច​ទៅ​កាន់​ទំព័រ​ចុង​ក្រោយ​នៃ​ឯកសារ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">បញ្ជា(Ctrl)<keycap>ចុង</keycap></keycombo> ឬ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>ទៅ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ទំព័រ​ចុង</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can go to the next page of the document using <keycap>Space</keycap>, "
#| "the <guibutton>Next Page</guibutton> Toolbar button or using <menuchoice> "
#| "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Page</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"You can go forward in the document using &Space; or &PgDn;. To go to the "
"next page of the document use the <guibutton>Next Page</guibutton> Toolbar "
"button or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Page</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"អ្នក​អាច​ទៅ​កាន់​ទំព័រ​បន្ទាប់​នៃ​ឯកសារ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <keycap>ដក​ឃ្លា</keycap> ប៊ូតុង​របារ​ឧបករណ៍ "
"<guibutton>ទំព័រ​បន្ទាប់</guibutton> ឬ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <menuchoice> <guimenu>ទៅ</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>ទំព័រ​បន្ទាប់</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can go to the previous page of the document using <keycap>Backspace</"
#| "keycap>, the <guibutton>Previous Page</guibutton> Toolbar button or using "
#| "<menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Page</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"You can go back in the document using &Backspace; or &PgUp;. To go to the "
"previous page of the document use <guibutton>Previous Page</guibutton> "
"Toolbar button or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous "
"Page</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"អ្នក​អាច​ទៅ​កាន់​ទំព័រ​មុន​នៃ​ឯកសារ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <keycap>លុប​ថយ​ក្រោយ</keycap> ប៊ូតុង​របារ​ឧបករណ៍ "
"<guibutton>ទំព័រ​មុន</guibutton> ឬ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <menuchoice> <guimenu>ទៅ</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>ទំព័រ​មុន</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go back to the positions in the document where you came from in a "
"chronological order. Consider &eg; reading the phrase <quote>As shown in "
"[15], …</quote>, and you want to know quickly lookup reference [15]. So you "
"click on it, and &okular; will jump to the list of references. Using "
"<keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo> or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar will "
"bring you back to exactly the position where you came from."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can go to the last page of the document using <keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;<keycap>End</keycap></keycombo> or using <menuchoice> "
#| "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Last Page</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"You can go forward in the document after the jumping back as described above "
"using <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo> or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"អ្នក​អាច​ទៅ​កាន់​ទំព័រ​ចុង​ក្រោយ​នៃ​ឯកសារ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">បញ្ជា(Ctrl)<keycap>ចុង</keycap></keycombo> ឬ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>ទៅ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ទំព័រ​ចុង</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can go to the last page of the document using <keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;<keycap>End</keycap></keycombo> or using <menuchoice> "
#| "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Last Page</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"You can go to the next match when searching using <keycap>F3</keycap> or "
"&Enter; (when the focus is on <guilabel>Find</guilabel> text field) keys or "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> menu item or move back to the previous match using "
"<keycombo>&Shift;<keysym>F3</keysym></keycombo> or <keycombo>&Shift;&Enter;</"
"keycombo> (when the focus is on <guilabel>Find</guilabel> text field) keys "
"or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Previous</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"អ្នក​អាច​ទៅ​កាន់​ទំព័រ​ចុង​ក្រោយ​នៃ​ឯកសារ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">បញ្ជា(Ctrl)<keycap>ចុង</keycap></keycombo> ឬ​ដោយ​ប្រើ <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>ទៅ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ទំព័រ​ចុង</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Presentation Mode"
msgstr "របៀប​បង្ហាញ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Presentation mode represents another way to view PDF documents in "
#| "&kpdf;. It can be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Presentation</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. It shows "
#| "the document on a page per page basis. The pages are shown with zoom to "
#| "page, that means all the page is visible."
msgid ""
"The Presentation mode represents another way to view documents in &okular;. "
"It can be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Presentation</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. It shows the "
"document on a page per page basis. The pages are shown with zoom to page, "
"that means all the page is visible."
msgstr ""
"របៀប​បង្ហាញ​តំណាង​ឲ្យ​វិធី​មួយ​ទៀត​ដើម្បី​មើល​ឯកសារ PDF ក្នុង Kpdf ។វា​អាច​ត្រូវ​បាន​បើក​ក្នុង "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>ការ​បង្ហាញ</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ។ វា​បង្ហាញ​ឯកសារ​នៅ​លើ​ទំព័រ​ក្នុង​ទំព័រ​មូលដ្ឋាន ។ ទំព័រ​ត្រូវ​បាន​បង្ហាញ​ជាមួយ​ការ​ពង្រី​ទៅ​"
"ទំព័រ ដែល​មាន​ន័យ​ថា​ទំព័រ​ទាំងអស់​អាច​មើល​ឃើញ ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "PDF documents can even specify that they are always opened in "
#| "presentation mode."
msgid ""
"&PDF; documents can even specify that they are always opened in presentation "
"mode."
msgstr "ឯកសារ PDF អាច​បញ្ជាក់​ថា ពួក​វា​ត្រូវ​បាន​បើក​ជានិច្ច​ក្នុង​របៀប​បង្ហាញ ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in presentation mode, you have an helper bar located on the top of the "
"screen. Just move the mouse cursor to the top of the screen to make it "
"appear."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:305
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>The configuration dialogue</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>&okular; in Presentation Mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>ប្រអប់​កំណត់​រចនា​សម្ព័ន្ធ</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:311
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>The configuration dialogue</phrase>"
msgid "<phrase>&okular; in Presentation Mode</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>ប្រអប់​ការ​កំណត់​រចនា​សម្ព័ន្ធ</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To navigate between pages you may use the &LMB; (next page) and the &RMB; "
#| "(previous page), the mouse wheel, the arrow icons that appear as soon as "
#| "you move the mouse cursor to the top of the screen, or the keys specified "
#| "in the <link linkend=\"navigating\">Navigating</link> section."
msgid ""
"To navigate between pages you may use the &LMB; (next page) and the &RMB; "
"(previous page), the mouse wheel, the arrow icons or the line edit in the "
"top bar, or the keys specified in the <link linkend=\"navigating"
"\">Navigating</link> section."
msgstr ""
"ដើម្បី​រុករក​រវាង​ទំព័រ​ដែល​អ្នក​អាច​ប្រើ​ប៊ូតុង​កណ្ដុរ​ឆ្វេង (ទំព័រ​បន្ទាប់) និង​ប៊ូតុង​កណ្ដុរ​ស្ដាំ (ទំព័រ​មុន) កង់​"
"កណ្ដុរ រូប​តំណាង​ព្រួញ ដែល​លេចឡើង​ពេល​អ្នក​ផ្លាស់ទី​ទស្សន៍​ទ្រនិច្ច​ទៅ​កំពូល​នៃ​អេក្រង់ ឬ​គ្រាប់​ចុច​ដែល​បញ្ជាក់​ក្នុង​"
"ផ្នែក <link linkend=\"navigating\">រុករក</link> ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Play/Pause</guilabel> button in the top bar to start playing "
"presentation or pause it, correspondingly."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can exit presentation mode at any time by pressing the <keycap>ESC</"
#| "keycap> key or clicking the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> icon appearing if you "
#| "move the mouse cursor to the top of the screen."
msgid ""
"You can exit presentation mode at any time by pressing the &Esc; key or "
"clicking the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> icon in the top bar."
msgstr ""
"អ្នក​អាច​បិទ​របៀប​ការ​បង្ហាញ​នៅ​ពេល​ណា​មួយ​ដោយ​ចុច​គ្រាប់​ចុច <keycap>គេច</keycap> ឬ​ដោយ​ចុច​រូប​តំណាង "
"<guiicon>ចេញ</guiicon> ដែល​លេចឡើង បើ​អ្នក​ផ្លាស់ទី​ទស្សន៍​ទ្រនិច​ទៅ​កំពូល​នៃ​អេក្រង់ ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also draw on the current page with a pencil. Click on the "
"<guilabel>Toggle Drawing Mode</guilabel> icon in the top bar to enable or "
"disable the possibility to draw in the presentation mode. The drawings are "
"cleared automatically when leaving the presentation mode. You can also click "
"on the <guilabel>Erase Drawings</guilabel> icon to remove the drawings in "
"the current page."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The presentation mode has support for more than one screen in a multi-"
"monitor configuration. With more than one screen a new button will appear in "
"the top bar, with the icon of a screen: this is a drop down box that allows "
"you to move the presentation to any of the other available screens."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Presentation mode has some configuration options, you can find their "
#| "description at <link linkend=\"configpresentation\">Configuring &kpdf;</"
#| "link>."
msgid ""
"Presentation mode has some configuration options, you can find their "
"description in the chapter <link linkend=\"configpresentation\">Configuring "
"&okular;</link>."
msgstr ""
"របៀប​បង្ហាញ​មាន​ជម្រើស​ការ​កំណត់​រចនា​សម្ព័ន្ធ​ខ្លះ អ្នក​អាច​រក​ការ​ពិពណ៌​នា​របស់​ពួក​វា​នៅ <link linkend="
"\"configpresentation\">កំណត់​រចនា​សម្ព័ន្ធ Kpdf</link> ។"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse Search between &latex; Editors and &okular;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inverse search is a very useful feature when you are writing a &latex; "
"document yourself. If everything is set up properly, you can click into "
"&okular;'s window with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"while pressing &Shift;. After that editor loads the &latex; source file and "
"jumps to the proper paragraph."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse search cannot work unless:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "The source file has been compiled successfully."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "&okular; knows which editor you would like to use."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Another way is to hold the &LMB; down at any place on the document while "
#| "dragging the mouse in the opposite direction of where you want to move. "
#| "This procedure only works if the Browse Tool is enabled, which you can "
#| "select by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Browse Tool </guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"The Browse tool has to be enabled, which you can select by choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Browse </guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"វិធី​មួយ​ទៀត​គឺ​សង្កត់​ប៊ូតុង​កណ្ដុរ​ឆ្វេង​នៅ​កន្លែង​ណា​មួយ​លើ​ឯកសារ ខណៈ​កំពុង​អូស​កណ្ដុរ​ក្នុង​ទិស​បញ្ច្រាស​នៃ​កន្លែង​ដែល​"
"អ្នក​ចង់​ផ្លាស់ទី ។ បែបបទ​នេះ​ធ្វើការ​តែ​បើ​ឧបករណ៍​រក​មើល​ត្រូវ​បាន​បើក ដែល​អ្នក​អាច​ជ្រើស​ដោយ​ជ្រើស "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>ឧបករណ៍</guimenu><guimenuitem>ឧបករណ៍​រក​មើល</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this feature of &okular;, a left mouse click while pressing &Shift; in "
"the &DVI; or &PDF; document will result in editor opening the corresponding "
"&latex; document and attempt to go to the corresponding line. Remember to "
"tell &okular; to use proper editor, in &okular;'s menu item "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Okular...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (on the page <guimenuitem>Editor</guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more details on editor configuration please refer to the <link linkend="
"\"configeditor\">corresponding section of this manual</link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
